This is the new code for the slot machine animation that will be implemented in the /demo page.

The animation includes:
1. A visual slot machine with three reels
2. Images that spin and stop on random selections
3. Animations for highlighting selected items
4. GSAP animations for smooth transitions
5. A final animation showing an "Offering Memorandum" image

The implementation will use Next.js components to properly integrate this with the Astroop CRE website.
